original_title: Chikara: Return Of The Son Of The International Invasion Of International Invaders - 1st Stage
overview: Lance Steel and Lance Steel fight in a “Loser Must Leave the Present” match that sees one knight banished to the past! Larry Sweeney and Eddie Kingston fight all over the Legion Hall! The only one-on-one match between Reckless Youth and Claudio Castagnoli is featured. Icarus teams with Gran Akuma and Chris Hero in an attempt at revenge against Jigsaw, Mike Quackenbush and Shane Storm!
title: Chikara: Return Of The Son Of The International Invasion Of International Invaders - 1st Stage
